1. Use the getProp text files to work with the build
2. Use the service list to mess about with what IInterfaces through the kernel.
3. Use IInterface classes directly like

    private ITelephony getITelephony() {
            return ITelephony.Stub.asInterface(ServiceManager.getService(Context.TELEPHONY_SERVICE));
        }

4. Look at http://www.programcreek.com/java-api-examples/index.php?source_dir=android_packages_apps_settings-master/src/com/android/settings/DeviceInfoSettings.java# for settings
5. Look at System.getProperties java for android return values